sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant EventManager
    participant LoggingObserver
    participant StatisticsObserver
    participant WebSocketObserver
    participant EmailObserver
    participant Database

    User->>Frontend: Register new account
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/auth/register
    Backend->>Database: Create user record
    Database-->>Backend: User created
    Backend->>EventManager: Emit USER_REGISTERED event
    EventManager->>LoggingObserver: Log registration
    LoggingObserver-->>EventManager: Logged
    EventManager->>StatisticsObserver: Update statistics
    StatisticsObserver-->>EventManager: Updated
    EventManager->>WebSocketObserver: No WebSocket clients
    EventManager->>EmailObserver: Send welcome email
    EmailObserver-->>EventManager: Email sent
    Backend-->>Frontend: Registration success
    Frontend-->>User: Show success message

    User->>Frontend: Create book exchange
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/exchanges
    Backend->>Database: Create exchange record
    Database-->>Backend: Exchange created
    Backend->>EventManager: Emit EXCHANGE_CREATED event
    EventManager->>LoggingObserver: Log exchange creation
    EventManager->>StatisticsObserver: Update exchange stats
    EventManager->>WebSocketObserver: Notify target user
    WebSocketObserver-->>EventManager: Notification sent
    Backend-->>Frontend: Exchange created
    Frontend-->>User: Show exchange status

    User->>Frontend: Send chat message
    Frontend->>Backend: WebSocket message
    Backend->>Database: Store message
    Database-->>Backend: Message stored
    Backend->>EventManager: Emit MESSAGE_SENT event
    EventManager->>LoggingObserver: Log message
    EventManager->>StatisticsObserver: Update message stats
    EventManager->>WebSocketObserver: Broadcast to participants
    WebSocketObserver-->>EventManager: Message broadcasted
    Backend-->>Frontend: Message delivered
    Frontend-->>User: Show message in chat

    User->>Frontend: Accept exchange
    Frontend->>Backend: PATCH /api/exchanges/{id}/accept
    Backend->>Database: Update exchange status
    Database-->>Backend: Status updated
    Backend->>EventManager: Emit EXCHANGE_ACCEPTED event
    EventManager->>LoggingObserver: Log acceptance
    EventManager->>StatisticsObserver: Update stats
    EventManager->>WebSocketObserver: Notify requester
    WebSocketObserver-->>EventManager: Notification sent
    EventManager->>EmailObserver: Send acceptance email
    EmailObserver-->>EventManager: Email sent
    Backend-->>Frontend: Exchange accepted
    Frontend-->>User: Show updated status

    User->>Frontend: Add friend
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/friends/{user_id}
    Backend->>Database: Create friendship
    Database-->>Backend: Friendship created
    Backend->>EventManager: Emit FRIEND_ADDED event
    EventManager->>LoggingObserver: Log friendship
    EventManager->>StatisticsObserver: Update friend stats
    EventManager->>WebSocketObserver: Notify new friend
    WebSocketObserver-->>EventManager: Notification sent
    Backend-->>Frontend: Friend added
    Frontend-->>User: Show success message
